		<div class="get-involved-content">
			<h3><span class="step">1.</span> Spread the word on Facebook</h3> 
			<ul>
				<li>Join our <strong><a target="_blank" href="http://www.facebook.com/Milaap.org">Facebook fan</a></strong> page, a great way to receive updates about Milaap and share your thoughts with us</li>
				<li>Click on "Suggest to Friends" on Milaap's Facebook fan page (in the top left corner), and then select which of your friends you want to tell about Milaap.</li>
				<li>Post interesting news/links you find about micro-finance, new financing models for education, energy, water etc.. This will help Milaap and your fellow Milaaprs (Milaap-likers) educate each other about the many interesting and important issues which affect and are affected by what we're doing.</li>
			</ul>
