			<h3><span class="step">2.</span> Spread the word on Twitter</h3> 
			<ul>
				<li>You can also follow us on Twitter <strong><a target="_blank" href="http://www.twitter.com/milaapdotorg">(@milaapdotorg)</a></strong></li>
				<li>Tweet about Milaap.org, and re-tweet our posts to share them with others (see here for more on how to use Twitter).</li>
			</ul>
